牌子<br />\n利申:用左兩三年tp-link除左setup小小煩未有過問題</blockquote><br />\n本身router係apple架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b5ddbae24d20ebab06ed2ae11c2c20bf031afd","tid":240073,"uid":7538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T07:21:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問homeplug 同wifi extender 有咩分別</blockquote><br />\nWifi extender係接收原本wifi訊號再repeat<br />\nhomeplug係靠電線<br />\n我個case真係唔多work 之前試過 隔左幅牆就唔掂"},{"pid":"e4cd04367238faba290d8e699b532133f6d14a82","tid":240073,"uid":7538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T07:22:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用過，好唔穩定同埋好熱，好快冇用驚火燭</blockquote><br />\n冇人叫你長插</blockquote><br />\n幾可有人屋企router會每日定時開關呀<br />\n大把人都係7*24開著 homeplug都係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nhomeplug要用先開都得既 我都間中先要出客廳用<br />\n但router真係長開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aaa7dcb13c20a6558a432185d8db5d76fdc4a51","tid":240073,"uid":43285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T07:24:11.000Z","msg":"homeplug要係新式大廈先好用<br />\n舊樓好鬼差"},{"pid":"ffcc7c82b61d4a18af56f5172e239e0cd6353167","tid":240073,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T07:25:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問homeplug 同wifi extender 有咩分別</blockquote><br />\n如果你個位收唔到wifi 咪要落homeplug <br />\n收到或者wifi差先可以落extender <br />\n但HomePlug 就冇咁嘅限制"},{"pid":"17de230c95c387edfbb976e503358881b88b14df","tid":240073,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T07:26:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用過，好唔穩定同埋好熱，好快冇用驚火燭</blockquote><br />\n冇人叫你長插</blockquote><br />\n幾可有人屋企router會每日定時開關呀<br />\n大把人都係7*24開著 homeplug都係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nRouter梗係長開啦<br />\nHomeplug要用先插 因為enable wifi真係會熱"},{"pid":"b1793f00042a90deac6ea979570b6e526894132d","tid":240073,"uid":114621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T07:27:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>homeplug要係新式大廈先好用<br />\n舊樓好鬼差</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係睇間屋電線咩 （利申：唔識9up）<br />\n我屋企一年前先裝修完鋪過晒電線<br />\n係我都知唔鋪埋lan線位好on9 但之前真係無諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2fd0df508599db6aa4ae9010509af8d80db3d0b","tid":240073,"uid":4174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T07:28:20.000Z","msg":"想問下有冇homeplug 可以代替埋router<br />\n即係廳到有modem 駁homeplug <br />\n房到直接插homeplug 出wifi 再用lan 線駁pc"},{"pid":"9a158e5dacc4fca1a8b998b11bbce4b5dc829d21","tid":240073,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T07:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用咩版子router就用番咩牌子 仲要全家同一個牌子<br />\n利申:用左兩三年tp-link除左setup小小煩未有過問題</blockquote><br />\n本身router係apple架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實樓主都用緊netvigator 1000m啦 <br />\n不如考慮轉個大功率少少嘅router 2.4G穿牆咪算囉<br />\nHome plug 都唔平"},{"pid":"bfe3360ca1080fabad886d60bc9bd7fc89869f67","tid":240073,"uid":7538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T07:32:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用咩版子router就用番咩牌子 仲要全家同一個牌子<br />\n利申:用左兩三年tp-link除左setup小小煩未有過問題</blockquote><br />\n本身router係apple架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實樓主都用緊netvigator 1000m啦 <br />\n不如考慮轉個大功率少少嘅router 2.4G穿牆咪算囉<br />\nHome plug 都唔平</blockquote><br />\n有咩選擇 放係房出到廳隔住左兩幅牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.